Read `.claude/rules/testing.md` for the full testing rules.

Key points: Vitest + `@testing-library/react`. Tests in `src/__tests__/`. Wrap components in `renderWithProviders()` for intl/theme context. Prefer `getByRole`/`getByLabelText` over `getByTestId`. Mock `@/lib/api-client` for network calls.
